summary: This document is a certification of good standing for the corporation MORT, INC., filed with the Office of the Lieutenant Governor in the Virgin Islands. It confirms that the corporation was incorporated on April 12, 2011, and is authorized to conduct business in the Virgin Islands.
locations: 5049 Kongons Gode, Charlotte Amalie, Virgin Islands 00802
keyFacts: The corporation MORT, INC. filed Articles of Incorporation on April 12, 2011.
A Certificate of Incorporation was issued on April 27, 2011.
The corporation is considered to be in good standing as of the date of this certification.
